{"tid":1382200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發多圖）小西灣有隻金毛藍屍奶撕官警黑poster！","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T19:36:21.000Z","uid":89031,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"adab586c4a027e884f6f1c066203d9300b224243","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時地 1925 藍灣往富欣方向天橋</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPosters 早幾日已經見到<br />\n內容係元朗官警黑勾結 都有唔少人睇<br />\n<br />\n今日經過見到件藍屍奶一路行一路撕<br />\n小妹感疑惑就停低查詢一下<br />\n<br />\n我：「請問係咪你黐？唔係你黐嘅你做咩撕？」<br />\n佢：「我喺呢度住客，我唔鍾意見到呢啲垃圾就有權撕！」<br />\n我：「你可以打1823投訴，但唔係你黐你冇權撕」<br />\n佢：（癲喪mode 見下圖）「呢啲係垃圾，全部都係垃圾！你咪影我囉！」<br />\n<br />\n好 我就影低你<br />\n有冇人認得依舊垃圾 應該住藍灣半島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dswx694.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdswx694.png&h=48a7ae02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcK7V3r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcK7V3r.png&h=36aee89e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwBBPot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwBBPot.png&h=ddecf1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MFi2Ju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MFi2Ju.png&h=ca3a990f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n唔係本人貼<br />\n但心痛手足一張張彩print俾人撕走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n其實班藍絲明未？<br />\n言論自由唔係唔俾人講嘢 有你講冇人講<br />\n你撐警奶共可以係我哋隔離貼撐警奶共<br />\n但唔係撕走我哋嘅聲音<br />\n你正一生番野蠻人 <br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n撕一貼百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"50f5dfbe2077765585d951710ba86bf77c75eb58","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"推到有人認得佢"},{"pid":"edbaa480523b5a3e89c95f5a5c8a8b89cac669e2","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"自推 推到有人認得條八婆！！！"},{"pid":"b690ddc8eea10e6636fd3c599c52f024427590da","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"ed0997e64826c4f8c3f00d79c715ab6fa1ae166e","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba2fc46cb1894ec0e0f4bc945b97dd5e9ef165b","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"e866c7d4be8f00d82392af7fe1f5d3339dcf888f","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:12:42.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人見到"},{"pid":"93bd3a1afb3103a251b096685f057331350528e2","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"c04b2267d98578dd0ae4e21cd32b5f48ccdbf487","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"推九"},{"pid":"feb70d61bebefcb17cbfe51f61fc1e84dbabad93","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"推十"},{"pid":"6e1b1879d044da4e0f2cebad5ad27005f4c041f7","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"018adcb597f8ca2040f78d637ab42aaf1bd963b2","tid":1382200,"uid":89031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af43167873fc59fc182